  "title": "A round white and yellow UFO was observed in Curitiba-PR [1993]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/06/a-round-white-and-yellow-ufo-was-observed-in-curitiba-pr-1993/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1pj",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 19th, 1993</strong>. Time: 20:00. Duration: 30 minutes. In Pinheirinho, Curitiba, State of Paraná, five people observed a small, round, white and yellow UFO between the South and the East regions of the city. According to the witnesses, the unidentified flying object moved at a slow speed in a straight path. The sighting occurred in a cloudy weather and with the naked eye.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.339. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Pinheirinho, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
